You may consider to use WET (windows easy transfer) and PickMeApp: two free solutions to migrate from XP to Windows 7 or to transfer yiur applications. WET may transfer your XP program settings to Win 7 while portable  PickMeApp tool may transfer programs from XP to XP and from XP to Windows 7. PickMeApp claims to support unlimited number of programs.
